---
# Rhodo Engine Core - Performance-Optimized Formatting
# Slightly relaxed for SIMD, cache alignment, and hot-path readability
BasedOnStyle: InheritParentConfig
Language: Cpp

# Slightly wider for performance-critical code with SIMD/intrinsics
ColumnLimit: 100

# Allow longer functions in engine code
AllowShortFunctionsOnASingleLine: Inline
AllowShortLambdasOnASingleLine: All

# Better for data-oriented design
AlignConsecutiveAssignments: Consecutive
AlignConsecutiveDeclarations: Consecutive

# More readable for low-level code
SpacesBeforeTrailingComments: 3

# Everything else inherits from root
...
